oto%2F107251601.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESiddharth%20Anand's%20action%20film%20%26quot%3BFighter%2C%26quot%3B%20starring%20Hrithik%20Roshan%2C%20Deepika%20Padukone%2C%20and%20Anil%20Kapoor%2C%20released%20with%20high%20expectations%20but%20witnessed%20a%20substantial%2072%25%20drop%20on%20Monday%2C%20collecting%20around%20Rs%208%20crore%20in%20India.%20This%20decline%20is%20more%20pronounced%20than%20Siddharth%20and%20Hrithik's%20previous%20collaborations%2C%20%26quot%3BWar%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BPathaan.%26quot%3B%20Despite%20the%20drop%2C%20%26quot%3BFighter%26quot%3B%20has%20a%20chance%20for%20revival.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fbox-office%2Fhrithik-roshans-fighter-witnesses-a-significant-drop-as-compared-to-war-and-pathaan-on-first-monday%2Farticleshow%2F107251601.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IBM%20Chief%20Arvind%20Krishna's%20Rule%20For%20Managers%3A%20Move%20Near%20Office%20Or%20Leave%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EInternational%20Business%20Machines%20Corp.%20delivered%20a%20companywide%20ultimatum%20to%20managers%20who%20are%20still%20working%20remotely%3A%20move%20near%20an%20office%20or%20leave%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20US%20managers%20must%20immediately%20report%20to%20an%20office%20or%20client%20location%20at%20least%20three%20days%20a%20week%20%26quot%3Bregardless%20of%20current%20work%20location%20status%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20a%20memo%20sent%20on%20Jan.%2016%20viewed%20by%20Bloomberg.%20Badge-in%20data%20will%20be%20used%20to%20%26quot%3Bassess%20individual%20presence%26quot%3B%20and%20shared%20with%20managers%20and%20human%20resources%2C%20Senior%20Vice%20President%20John%20Granger%20wrote%20in%20the%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20working%20remotely%2C%20other%20than%20employees%20with%20exceptions%20such%20as%20medical%20issues%20or%20military%20service%2C%20who%20don't%20live%20close%20enough%20to%20commute%20to%20a%20facility%20must%20relocate%20near%20an%20IBM%20office%20by%20the%20start%20of%20August%2C%20according%20to%20the%20memo.%20That%20generally%20means%20within%2050%20miles%20(80%20kilometers)%2C%20according%20to%20a%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20rule%20who%20asked%20not%20to%20be%20identified%20speaking%20about%20corporate%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManagers%20who%20don't%20agree%20to%20relocate%20and%20are%20unable%20to%20secure%20a%20role%20that's%20approved%20to%20be%20remote%20must%20%26quot%3Bseparate%20from%20IBM%2C%26quot%3B%20Granger%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIBM%20is%20focused%20on%20providing%20a%20work%20environment%20that%20balances%20flexibility%20with%20the%20face-to-face%20interactions%20that%20make%20us%20more%20productive%2C%20innovative%20and%20better%20able%20to%20serve%20our%20clients%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20company%20spokesperson%20said.%20%26quot%3BConsistent%20with%20that%20approach%2C%20we're%20requiring%20executives%20and%20people%20managers%20in%20the%20United%20States%20to%20be%20in%20the%20office%20at%20least%20three%20days%20per%20week.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Executive%20Office%20Arvind%20Krishna%20has%20long%20touted%20the%20importance%20of%20in-person%20work.%20In%20a%20May%202023%20interview%20with%20Bloomberg%2C%20Krishna%20said%20that%20promotions%20will%20be%20rarer%20for%20those%20who%20aren't%20on-site.%20Some%20teams%20within%20IBM%20had%20already%20instituted%20office%20attendance%20requirements.%20A%20November%20memo%20told%20employees%20in%20the%20infrastructure%20business%20unit%20to%20show%20up%20at%20company%20locations%20at%20least%20three%20days%20a%20week%20with%20%26quot%3Bmanagers%20and%20executives%20expected%20to%20be%20in%20more.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIBM%20has%20slimmed%20its%20operations%20to%20focus%20on%20software%20and%20services%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20introduced%20new%20products%20to%20capitalize%20on%20interest%20in%20artificial%20intelligence%20and%20divested%20its%20managed%20infrastructure%2C%20weather%20and%20health%20businesses.%20Executives%20gave%20a%20positive%20outlook%20for%202024%20with%20fourth-quarter%20earnings%20last%20week%2C%20sending%20shares%20to%20their%20best%20day%20in%20almost%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBig%20Blue%20expects%20to%20reduce%20jobs%20this%20year%2C%20spending%20a%20similar%20amount%20on%20restructuring%20as%20it%20did%20last%20year%20when%20it%20planned%20to%20cut%203%2C900%20workers%2C%20Chief%20Financial%20Officer%20James%20Kavanaugh%20said%20last%20week.%20Return-to-office%20mandates%20are%20often%20seen%20as%20fueling%20attrition.%20IBM%20had%20about%20288%2C000%20workers%20globally%20at%20the%20end%20of%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20closed%20a%20number%20of%20offices%20since%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20potentially%20complicating%20return-to-office%20plans%20for%20workers%2C%20including%20facilities%20in%20Philadelphia%2C%20central%20New%20York%20State%2C%20Southbury%2C%20Connecticut%2C%20and%20Iowa.%20Reducing%20its%20real%20estate%20footprint%20is%20part%20of%20IBM's%20ongoing%20margin-expansion%20efforts%2C%20Kavanaugh%20said%20during%20an%20earnings%20call%20last%20week.%20It%20couldn't%20be%20determined%20how%20many%20managers%20would%20be%20required%20to%20move%20under%20the%20new%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20companies%20have%20increased%20return-to-office%20requirements%20over%20the%20last%20year%2C%20replacing%20employee-friendly%20incentives%20like%20happy%20hours%20and%20commuter%20subsidies%20with%20more%20punitive%20measures%20including%20disciplinary%20action%20or%20limited%20career%20advancement%20if%20attendance%20targets%20aren't%20met.%20The%20tech%20industry%20in%20particular%20has%20seen%20tightening%20rules%20as%20the%20market%20soured%20and%20the%20risk%20of%20job%20cuts%20has%20tipped%20the%20scale%20in%20favor%20of%20employers.%20Amazon.com%20Inc.%20and%20AT%26amp%3BT%20Inc.%20have%20each%20ordered%20some%20remote%20workers%20to%20relocate%20near%20offices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20new%20rules%2C%20office%20attendance%20remained%20fairly%20stagnant%20throughout%202023%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20Kastle%20Systems.%20Across%20the%2010%20largest%20business%20districts%20in%20the%20US%2C%20the%20number%20of%20workers%20in%20the%20office%20hovered%20around%2050%25%20of%20what%20it%20was%20before%20the%20pandemic%2C%20with%20tech-heavy%20regions%20like%20the%20San%20Francisco%20Bay%20Area%20reporting%20even%20lower%20percentages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706595000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fhgj0jvi8_ibm-generic_625x300_30_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fibm-chief-arvind-krishnas-rule-for-managers-move-near-office-or-leave-4958494%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22International%20Business%20Machines%20Corp.%20delivered%20a%20companywide%20ultimatum%20to%20managers%20who%20are%20still%20working%20remotely%3A%20move%20near%20an%20office%20or%20leave%20the%20company.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fibm-chief-arvind-krishnas-rule-for-managers-move-near-office-or-leave-4958494%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fibm-chief-arvind-krishnas-rule-for-managers-move-near-office-or-leave-4958494%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fibm-chief-arvind-krishnas-rule-for-managers-move-near-office-or-leave-4958494%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Plane%20Parked%2C%20BMW%20Seized%2C%20Phones%20Off%3A%20Search%20For%20'Missing'%2