%20from%20the%20Office%20of%20the%20Dean%20of%20Students%20confirming%20Acharya's%20death.%20%26quot%3BA%20deceased%20person%20was%20found%20that%20matched%20Neel's%20description%20and%20had%20Neel's%20ID%20on%20(him)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcharya%20was%20a%20double%20major%20in%20computer%20science%20and%20data%20science%20in%20the%20John%20Martinson%20Honors%20College%2C%20according%20to%20the%20email.%20His%20friend%20and%20roommate%20Aryan%20Khanolkar%20said%20he%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bloving%2C%20charismatic%20soul%2C%20and%20will%20be%20cherished%20by%20all%20of%20us%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Neel%20Acharya's%20LinkedIn%20profile%2C%20he%20completed%20his%20schooling%20in%20Pune%20and%20joined%20Purdue%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20mother%20Gaury%20on%20Sunday%20put%20out%20a%20Twitter%20post%2C%20informing%20that%20Acharya%20had%20been%20missing%20and%20was%20last%20seen%20by%20an%20Uber%20driver%20who%20dropped%20him%20at%20the%20campus.%20She%20sought%20help%20in%20finding%20him.%20Soon%20after%2C%20Acharya%20was%20confirmed%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20incident%20comes%20close%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20the%20brutal%20murder%20of%20another%20Indian%20student%20in%20the%20US.%20Vivek%20Saini%2C%20who%20was%20pursuing%20an%20MBA%20course%20in%20Georgia's%20Lithonia%2C%20worked%20part-time%20at%20a%20convenience%20store%20that%20sheltered%20a%20homeless%20man%20Julian%20Faulkner.%20Saini%20had%20reportedly%20given%20the%20man%20chips%2C%20water%20and%20even%20a%20jacket.%20On%20January%2016%2C%20the%2025-year-old%20reportedly%20refused%20to%20give%20Faulkner%20free%20food%20and%20this%20led%20to%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706593920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F213ld2r_neel-acharya_625x300_30_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fneel-acharya-purdue-university-driven-talented-us-university-in-shock-over