0exercising%20%3Cem%3Esuo%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Emotu%3C%2Fem%3E%20powers%2C%20initiated%20proceedings%20following%20an%20order%20by%20Justice%20Abhijit%20Gangopadhyay%20of%20the%20Calcutta%20HC%2C%20which%20disregarded%20a%20stay%20imposed%20by%20a%20division%20bench.%20This%20division%20bench%2C%20led%20by%20Justices%20Soumen%20Sen%20and%20Uday%20Kumar%2C%20had%20halted%20the%20CBI%20investigation%2C%20stating%20that%20the%20state%20government%20should%20complete%20its%20inquiry%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Cspan%3Especial%20Saturday%20hearing%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20temporarily%20halted%20proceedings%20in%20the%20single%20bench%E2%80%99s%20writ%20petition%20and%20the%20division%20bench%E2%80%99s%20Letters%20of%20Patent%20Appeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Letter%20of%20Patent%20Appeal%20is%20a%20petition%20against%20a%20single%20judge%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20a%20different%20bench%20of%20the%20same%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Fpdf_upload%2F41222024150149991order29-jan-2024-519077.pdf%5C%22%3EOn%20January%2030%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0apex%20court%20judges%20did%20not%20comment%20on%20the%20apparent%20clash%20between%20Justices%20Gangopadhyay%20and%20Sen%2C%20observing%20that%20any%20remark%20would%20demean%20the%20dignity%20of%20a%20high%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CCasting%20aspersions%20on%20a%20single%20judge%20or%20division%20bench%20would%20not%20be%20proper.%20Anything%20we%20say%20will%20affect%20the%20dignity%20of%20the%20High%20Court.%20We%20will%20handle%20it%20in%20some%20way.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20five-judge%20bench%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20headed%20by%20the%20CJI%2C%20decided%20to%20transfer%20the%20entire%20matter%20to%20itself%2C%20scheduling%20it%20for%20a%20three-week%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20hearin