%20official%20bought%20a%20sex%20doll%20for%20a%20tourist%20exhibition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20doll%2C%20which%20cost%20over%20%242%2C800%2C%20was%20clad%20in%20a%20kimono%20and%20displayed%20at%20an%20airport.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAuditors%20said%20the%20doll%20was%C2%A0%26quot%3Bextremely%20expensive%26quot%3B%20and%C2%A0%26quot%3Bgrossly%20inappropriate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAuditors%20have%20rapped%20the%20Tokushima%20Prefectural%20Government%20for%20purchasing%20an%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20expensive%26quot%3B%20sex%20doll%20to%20promote%20the%20city's%20tourism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20government's%20tourism%20policy%20division%20said%20it%20paid%20424%2C440%20Japanese%20yen%2C%20or%20%242%2C880%2C%20for%20the%20doll%2C%20which%20was%20used%20in%20a%20tourist%20exhibition%20at%20the%20Tokushima%20Awaodori%20Airport%20in%202017%2C%20per%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmainichi.jp%2Fenglish%2Farticles%2F20240129%2Fp2a%2F00m%2F0na%2F010000c%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMainichi%20Shimbun%3C%2Fa%3E%20report%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20exhibition%20was%20meant%20to%20promote%20the%20prefecture's%20traditional%20indigo-dyeing%20art%2C%20so%20the%20doll%20was%20clad%20in%20an%20indigo-dyed%20summer%20kimono%2C%20per%20the%20Mainichi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOfficials%20initially%20used%20a%20pair%20of%20cheaper%20mannequins%20%E2%80%94%20not%20the%20sex%20doll%20%E2%80%94%20at%20the%20exhibition%20in%20June%202017.%20Rental%20for%20both%20mannequins%20cost%20around%20%24180%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Mainichi%20Shimbun's%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20July%2C%20an%20unnamed%20male%20official%20decided%20to%20replace%20the%20mannequins%20with%20the%20sex%20doll.%20He%20then%20went%20about%20procuring%20the%20sex%20doll%2C%20which%20he'd%20concluded%20would%20be%20a%20crowd-pleaser%2C%20according%20to%20an%20audit%20report%20of%20the%20case%20obtained%20by%20the%20Mainichi%20Shimbun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20auditors%20dismissed%20the%20prefecture's%20claims%20that%20the%20sex%20doll%20was%20more%20effective%20at%20drawing%20tourists%20than%20the%20mannequins.%20The%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20expensive%26quot%3B%20doll%2C%20auditors%20said%20in%20their%20report%2C%20was%20%26quot%3Bgrossly%20inappropriate%20in%20terms%20of%20social%20norms.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20auditors%20have%20asked%20the%20prefecture%20to%20seek%20compensation%20from%20the%20officials%20involved%20in%20the%20purchase%20by%20June%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20this%20is%20a%20case%20from%20before%20my%20tenure%20as%20governor%2C%20as%20the%20figure%20in%20charge%20of%20appointments%2C%20I%20will%20take%20the%20audit%20results%20seriously%20and%20handle%20them%20in%20a%20strict%20manner%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20prefecture's%20governor%2C%20Masazumi%20Gotoda%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20the%20first%20time%20Japanese%20officials%20have%20courted%20controversy%20with%20odd%20buys%20using%20government%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%202021%2C%20officials%20in%20the%20seaside%20town%20of%20Noto%20were%20slammed%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapanese-town-covid-relief-cash-build-43-foot-squid-statue-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espending%20nearly%20%24170%2C000%20on%20a%20giant%20squid%20statue%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Officials%20financed%20the%20statue%20using%20part%20of%20the%20%245.4%20million%20in%20grants%20it%20received%20for%20COVID-19%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20the%20national%20government%20said%20funds%20could%20be%20used%20to%20enhance%20the%20region's%20appeal%2C%20we%20thought%20it%20would%20be%20good%20to%20make%20something%20with%20impact%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20unnamed%20official%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.yahoo.co.jp%2Farticles%2Fcf5eef54be6158595485a2af82b0a9e5a48d169f%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYahoo%20Japan%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BIt%20will%20promote%20our%20town%20and%20have%2