20for%20him%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20cornerstone%20of%20swaraj%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Hindutva%20project%20from%20the%201980s%20onwards%20transformed%20Ram%20into%20a%20virulent%20crusader%20of%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20Hindus%20against%20the%20minorities.%20In%20contrast%2C%20Gandhi%20stood%20for%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eminority%20rights%2C%20religious%20freedom%2C%20justice%20and%20forgiveness%E2%80%9D%20and%20is%20one%20who%20sacrificed%20his%20life%20for%20communal%20amity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20this%20contrast%20in%20values%20between%20Gandhi%20and%20Hindutva%20forces%20and%20the%20symbolic%20contest%20of%20rights%20over%20the%20meaning%2C%20value%20and%20mobilising%20of%20the%20figure%20of%20Ram%20that%20Kamal%20Haasan%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHey%20Ram%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(2000)%20is%20concerned%20with.%20While%20the%20last%20words%20of%20Gandhi%20address%20his%20personal%20God%2C%20in%20the%20film%2C%20it%20is%20also%20a%20cry%20of%20dismay%20at%20the%20atrocities%20committed%20in%20his%20God%E2%80%99s%20name%20that%20Ram%20would%20never%20have%20accepted.%20The%20cry%20is%20also%20a%20conscience%20raiser%20and%20can%20be%20seen%20as%20poignantly%20suggestive%20of%20how%20we%20have%20killed%20the%20Ram%20within%20us%20by%20becoming%20complicit%20with%20Hindutva%20ideological%20forces.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20cry%20thus%20designates%20both%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20horror%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20outrages%20man%20can%20commit%20on%20man%20and%20also%20constitutes%20an%20appeal%20to%20bring%20those%20%E2%80%9Chorrors%E2%80%9D%20to%20an%20end.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30104823%2Fmaxresdefault.jp