ople%20to%20stand%20up%20and%20be%20counted.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20go%20down%20to%20the%20wire%2C%20on%20what%20each%20of%20the%20numbers%20unveiled%20mean.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWho%20are%20the%20people%20referred%20to%20by%20percentages%20in%20the%20survey%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EToday%20we%20look%20at%20Bakkho%20(36%2C830)%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20society%20based%20on%20the%20principle%20of%20superiority%20by%20birth%2C%20people%20born%20with%20the%20stigma%20of%20untouchability%20are%20discriminated%20against%20at%20birth%20itself.%20No%20one%20can%20remain%20unaffected%20by%20it.%20For%20example%2C%20there%20is%20a%20caste%20group%20%E2%80%93%20Bakkho%20%E2%80%93%20whose%20members%20are%20citizens%20of%20this%20country%20like%20the%20Brahmins%2C%20Rajputs%2C%20Kayasthas%2C%20Yadavs%2C%20Dhobis%20and%20Paswans.%20However%2C%20their%20national%20population%20cannot%20be%20estimated%20because%20they%20were%20not%20even%20mentioned%20in%20the%20last%20declared%20caste%20census%20which%20was%20conducted%20in%201931.%20In%20the%201901%20census%2C%20however%2C%20they%20did%20find%20mention.%20A%20long%20time%20has%20passed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20271px)%2085vw%2C%20271px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22271%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%20838w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-210x300.jpg%20210w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-715x1024.jpg%20715w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682410%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22388%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20caste%20survey%20report%20in%20Bihar%20has%20revealed%20that%20the%20population%20of%20Bakkho%20caste%20group%20is%20only%2036%2C830.%20Although%20it%20can%20be%20assumed%20that%20the%20people%20of%20group%20are%20present%20in%20Pakistan%20and%20Bangladesh%20as%20well%20as%20in%20Indian%20states%20like%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20West%20Bengal%2C%20nothing%20concrete%20can%20be%20claimed%20about%20them%20in%20terms%20of%20statistics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGenerally%2C%20Bakkho%20are%20people%20who%20do%20not%20have%20a%20roof%20over%20their%20heads%20and%20live%20like%20nomads.%20Similar%20castes%20are%20included%20in%20nomadic%2C%20semi-nomadic%20and%20non-notified%20categories.%20But%20Bakkho%20is%20not%20one%20of%20them.%20In%20Bihar%2C%20they%20are%20included%20in%20the%20Extremely%20Backward%20Class%20category.%20This%20is%20because%20the%20people%20of%20Bakkho%20caste%20group%20have%20left%20their%20nomadic%20style%20of%20living%20and%20established%20permanent%20settlements.%20They%20work%20as%20agricultural%20labourers%20in%20addition%20to%20their%20traditional%20work.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20traditional%20occupation%20of%20the%20Bakkho%20caste%20group%20is%20completely%20unique%20because%20of%20the%20joviality%20involved%20in%20it.%20Owing%20to%20their%20cheerful%20nature%20they%20reach%20people%E2%80%99s%20doorsteps%20on%20every%20joyous%20occasion%20and%20sing%20songs%20of%20happiness.%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20they%20do%20not%20differentiate%20between%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims.The%20women%20in%20Bakkho%20families%20support%20the%20men%20in%20this%20work%20and%20are%20referred%20to%20as%20%E2%80%98Bakkhoin.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%2C%20people%20mostly%20donated%20grains%2C%20clothes%20and%20cash.%20Bakkhos%20would%20sometimes%20become%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-bhishti%5C%22%3EBhishtis%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20serve%20water%20or%20clean%20roads%20and%20drains.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20times%20changed.%20Earlier%20people%20used%20to%20request%20Bakkho%20people%20to%20visit%20their%20houses%20and%20sing%20for%20them.%20Many%20even%20offered%20land%20as%20gift%20in%20addition%20to%20money.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20these%20nomadic%20people%20found%20a%20place%20to%20live.%20But%20such%20appreciation%20is%20now%20rare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmong%20Hindus%2C%20a%20similar%20caste%20group%20is%20called%20Nutt.%20On%20the%20occasion%20of%20Chhath%2C%20childless%20women%20request%20them%20to%20dance%20to%20bring%20good%20tidings.%20This%20is%20called%20the%20Natua%20dance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20the%20Bakkhos%20have%20given%20up%20playing%20the%20Khanjari%2C%20a%20frame%20drum%2C%20and%20have%20also%20stopped%20singing%20songs.%20Instead%2C%20they%20work%20as%20daily%20wage%20labourers.%20One%20might%20encounter%20them%20carrying%20utensils%20and%20old%20clothes%20in%20baskets%20over%20their%20heads.%20Sometimes%2C%20in%20remote%20rural%20areas%20of%20Bihar%2C%20their%20melodious%20voices%20can%20still%20be%20heard.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20Hindi%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%20Read%20the%20Hindi%20original%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F262746%2Fbihar-caste-survey-bakkho-caste-society%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20earlier%20parts%20of%20the%20series%20on%20the%20following%20communities%20by%20clicking%20on%20their%20names%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-ghasi%5C%22%3EGhasi%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-santrash%5C%22%3ESantrash%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%7C%20%3Ca%2