aq%20wrote%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ECongratulations%20brother%20So%20Happy%20for%20you%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FTDmKXMZYjj%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FTDmKXMZYjj%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Imam%20Ul%20Haq%20(%40ImamUlHaq12)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FImamUlHaq12%2Fstatus%2F1751980432902455341%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2029%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20injuries%2C%20Jadeja%20sustained%20a%20hamstring%20problem%20while%20going%20for%20a%20quick%20single%20on%20Sunday%20while%20Rahul%20complained%20of%20pain%20in%20his%20right%20quadriceps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorryingly%2C%20Rahul%20had%20also%20injured%20his%20right%20thigh%20while%20fielding%20in%20the%20IPL%20in%20May%20last%20year%20and%20that%20required%20a%20surgery%2C%20keeping%20him%20out%20of%20the%20game%20for%20four%20months.%20%26quot%3BMr%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20and%20Mr%20KL%20Rahul%20have%20been%20ruled%20out%20of%20the%20second%20IDFC%20First%20Bank%20Test%20against%20England%20in%20Vizag%2C%20starting%20February%2002%2C%202024%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BCCI%20said%20in%20a%20media%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BCCI%20Medical%20Team%20is%20monitoring%20the%20progress%20of%20the%20duo%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Virat%20Kohli%20already%20unavailable%20for%20the%20first%20two%20Tests%20due%20to%20personal%20reasons%2C%20the%20injuries%20to%20Jadeja%20and%20Rahul%20have%20made%20matters%20worse%20for%20India%2C%20who%20find%20themselves%20under%20pressure%20after%20losing%20only%20their%20fourth%20Test%20at%20home%20since%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Rahul%20and%20Jadeja%20had%20made%20significant%20contributions%20in%20the%20first%20Test%20before%20England%20staged%20a%20remarkable%20comeback%20to%20win%20the%20game%20by%2028%20run