%3Cem%3EToday%2C%20January%2030%2C%20is%20the%20anniversary%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20assassination.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%2C%20two%20temples%20%E2%80%93%20Birla%20Mandir%20and%20Valmiki%20Mandir%20%E2%80%93%20on%20Mandir%20Marg%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20New%20Delhi%20proved%20to%20be%20his%20laboratory%20to%20fight%20against%20the%20despicable%20practice%20of%20untouchability%20and%20scourge%20of%20caste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahatma%20Gandhi%20inaugurated%20Birla%20Mandir%20on%20March%2012%2C%201939.%20He%20inaugurated%20the%20temple%20on%20the%20condition%20that%20people%20of%20all%20castes%20would%20be%20allowed%20to%20enter%20there.%20There%20is%20a%20plaque%20on%20the%20main%20gate%20of%20Birla%20Mandir%20announcing%20that%20anyone%20can%20enter%20this%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%20was%20committed%20to%20the%20rights%20of%20so-called%20lower%20caste%20Hindus%20and%20wanted%20commitment%20from%20the%20Birla%20family%20that%20entry%20in%20this%20temple%20would%20not%20be%20restricted%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20caste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%20there%20must%20not%20be%20any%20ban%20on%20any%20community%20in%20temples%20of%20learning%2C%20as%20well%20as%20temples%20of%20worship.%20He%20wrote%20in%20the%20journal%20he%20started%2C%20%3Cem%3EYoung%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EIndia%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20April%2C%201925%3A%20%E2%80%9CTemples%2C%20public%20wells%20and%20schools%20must%20be%20open%20to%20Untouchables%20equally%20along%20with%20caste%20Hindus.%E2%80%9D%20He%20also%20started%20the%20journal%20%3Cem%3EHarijan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20through%20which%20he%20advocated%20his%20ideas.%20He%20called%20the%20practice%20of%20untouchability%20a%20moral%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20just%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20Mandir%20Marg%2C%20Gandhi%20had%20stayed%20for%20214%20days%20from%20April%201%2C%201946%20to%C2%A0%20June%2010%2C%201947%20with%20Valmikis.%20That%20was%20perhaps%20the%20first%20and%20only%20time%20when%20he%20became%20a%20teacher%20in%20true%20sense%20of%20the%20word.%20Of%20course%2C%20he%20knew%20that%20the%20life%20of%20Valmikis%20can%20transform%20only%20through%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20391px)%2085vw%2C%20391px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30085540%2FIMG-20240129-WA0015.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22391%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30085540%2FIMG-20240129-WA0015.jpg%20391w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30085540%2FIMG-20240129-WA0015-235x300.jpg%20235w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-694856%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EB.%20Louis%20Fischer%20with%20Gandhi%20at%20the%20Valmiki%20Mandir%20campus.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Gandhi%20moved%20to%20Valmiki%20Mandir%2C%20a%20very%20large%20number%20of%20Valmiki%20families%20used%20to%20live%20in%20the%20slums%20there.%20They%20worked%20as%20sweepers%20in%20areas%20like%20Gole%20Market%2C%20Irwin%20Road%20(now%20Baba%20Kharak%20Singh%20Marg)%20and%20Connaught%20Place.%20Once%20Gandhi%20shifted%20to%20the%20Valmiki%20colony%2C%20he%20started%20interacting%20with%20Valmiki%20families%20as%20well.%20He%20was%20shocked%20that%20they%20were%20all%20illiterate.%20Nobody%20had%20even%20stepped%20into%20a%20school.%20Then%20he%20asked%20local%20residents%20to%20send%20their%20kids%20to%20him%20so%20he%20could%20teach%20them.%20Elders%20started%20sending%20their%20kids%20in%20his%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrishan%20Vidyarthi%2C%20the%20caretaker%20and%20priest%20of%20Valmiki%20Mandir%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CGandhi%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20ensured%20that%20his%20classes%20took%20place%20both%20in%20the%20morning%20and%20evening%20without%20fail.%20He%20was%20such%20a%20conscientious%20teacher%20that%20he%20often%20used%20to%20delay%20his%20meetings%20with%20stalwarts%20of%20the%C2%A0%20freedom%20movement%20in%20order%20to%20finish%20his%20classes.%20Those%20classes%20would%20start%20before%20prayers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELouis%20Fischer%20in%20his%20brilliant%20biography%20of%20Gandhi%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Life%20of%20Mahatma%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewrote%2C%20%E2%80%9COnce%20I%20reached%20at%20the%20Valmiki%20temple%20from%20my%20hotel%20Imperial%20to%20interview%20him.%20But%2C%20he%20met%20me%20only%20after%20the%20prayers.%E2%80%9D%20Fischer%20had%20spent%20over%20one%20month%20in%20Delhi%20to%20collect%20notes%20for%20his%20biography%20in%201946.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%20was%20a%20hard%20task%20master.%20He%20used%20to%20chide%20students%20if%20any%20of%20them%20attended%20his%20class%20without%20having%20taken%20a%20bath.%20Not%20only%20the%20residents%20of%20Valmiki%20Colony%2C%20many%C2%A0%20students%20studying%20in%C2%A0%20schools%20like%20Raisina%20Bengali%20School%2C%20Harcourt%20Butler%20School%20and%20Delhi%20Tamil%20Education%20Association%20School%20also%20attended%20his%20classes%20from%20time%20to%20time.%20It%20was%20free%20for%20all.%20It%20is%20said%20that%20he%20knew%20all%20students%20by%20their%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20lucky%20students%20of%20Bapu%20are%20not%20around%20to%20narrate%20their%20experiences%2C%20but%20their%20kids%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmewat-flames-gandhijis-visit-1947%5C%22%3EWith%20Mewat%20in%20Flames%2C%20Remembering%20Gandhiji%E2%80%99s%20Visit%20to%20the%20Region%20in%201947%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20visit%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20small%20room%20inside%20the%20Valmiki%20temple%2C%20you%20would%20see%20several%20old%20sepia%20coloured%20photographs%20of%20him%20with%20Lord%20Mountbatten%20and%20Lady%20Mountbatten%2C%20Acharya%20Kriplani%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98Frontier%20Gandhi%E2%80%99%20Abdul%20Ghaffar%20Khan%2C%20C.%20Rajagopalachari%2C%20Sardar%20Patel%2C%20Maulana%20Azad%20and%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20one%20painting%20would%20tell%20you%20the%20story%20of%20this%20venerable%20room.%20In%20this%20fading%20painting%2C%20several%20kids%20are%20talking%20to%20Bapu%20in%20a%20very%20animated%20manner.%20While%20the%20name%20of%20the%20painter%20is%20not%20there%2C%20but%20he%20has%20done%20wonderful%20job%20to%20reflect%20the%20mood%20of%20the%20room%20with%20a%20great%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20in%20this%20carpeted%20room%2C%20you%20would%20also%20find%20a%20wooden%20desk%20in%20the%20centre%20that%20Gandhi%20used%20to%20write%20on.%20And%20on%20its%20right%20is%20the%20bed%20that%20Gandhi%20would%20use.%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20charkha%20is%20also%20there%2C%20close%20to%20his%20bed.%20Everything%20is%20where%20he%20left%20it%2C%20in%20the%20same%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrishan%20Vidyarthi%2C%2063%2C%20cleans%20Bapu%E2%80%99s%20classroom%20and%20blackboard%20there%20daily%20without%20fail.%20It%20is%20here%20that%20his%20ancestors%20used%20to%20study%20more%20than%2075%20years%20ago.%20For%20Krishan%2C%20this%20room%20is%20a%20sacred%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COf%20course%20it%20is%20not%20an%20ordinary%20classroom.%20My%20father%20was%20also%20taught%20by%20Gandhi%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20Krishan%20says%2C%20while%20preparing%20for%20the%20all-religion%20prayer%20that%20takes%20place%20outside%20the%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%20classes%20ended%20when%20he%20left%20for%20Birla%20House%20a%20couple%20of%20miles%20away%20from%20here%20on%20the%20advice%20of%20Nehru%20and%20Sardar%20Patel%2C%20as%20Hindu%20and%20Sikh%20refugees%20from%20Pakistan%20had%20started%20living%20on%20the%20campus%20of%20the%20Valmiki%20temple%20after%20the%20Partition%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EVivek%20Shukla%20is%20a%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706588041000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30085548%2FIMG-20240129-WA0014.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fgandhi-valmiki-temple-birla-caste%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shortly%20after%20Gandhi%20moved%20to%20Valmiki%20Mandir%2C%20he%20used%20to%20take%20classes%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20educate%20local%20children.%20Their%20sons%20and%20daughters%20recount%20the%20effort%20with%20fondness.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fgandhi-valmiki-temple-birla-caste%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%225%20of%20the%20wildest%20conspiracy%20theories%20behind%20Amelia%20Earhart's%20disappearance%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22amelia%20earhart%20and%20fred%20noonan%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5af2f319fb7ee218008b4628%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAmelia%20Earhart%20(L)%20with%20her%20navigator%2C%20Captain%20Fred%20Noonan%2C%20in%201937.%3Cp%3ETopical%20Press%20Agency%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famelia-earhart-disappearance-explained-photo-national-archives-history-2017-7%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famelia-earhart-disappearance-explained-photo-national-archives-history-2017-7%5C%22%3EAmelia%20Earhart%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0was%20one%20of%20the%20most%20famous%20aviators%20in%20the%20world%20when%20she%20vanished%20in%201937.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHer%20disappearance%20is%20among%20the%20greatest%20mysteries%20of%20all%20time%2C%20spurring%20many%20conspiracy%20theories.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHe