rifices%20to%20keep%20the%20nation%20united.%20You%20do%20not%20have%20that%20courage.%20Indira%20Gandhi%20was%20aware%20of%20the%20danger%20on%20her%20life.%20Still%2C%20she%20did%20not%20get%20freighted.%20Indira%20Ji%20in%20her%20last%20speech%20in%20Odisha%20had%20indicated%20about%20the%20danger%20to%20her%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kharge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20was%20her%20fault%2C%20Kharge%20asked%20adding%20had%20she%20looted%20anyone%3F%20%26quot%3BNo%2C%20she%20had%20all%20along%20worked%20to%20keep%20the%20nation%20united.%20But%20some%20people%20killed%20her.%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20also%20sacrificed%20his%20life%20while%20following%20his%20mother's%20footsteps.%20Rajiv%20Ji%20was%20killed%20by%20a%20human%20bomb.%20For%20what%20did%20he%20died%3F%20He%20died%20for%20the%20nation%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kharge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20returning%20to%20the%20NDA%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20claimed%20it%20will%20not%20have%20any%20impact%20on%20the%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20person%20quitting%20Mahagathbandhan%20will%20not%20weaken%20us.%20We%20will%20defeat%20the%20BJP%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20president%20also%20described%20PM%20Modi%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bhabitual%20liar%26quot%3B%20whom%20he%20accused%20of%20misleading%20the%20people%20by%20assuring%20two%20crore%20jobs%20every%20year%20and%20Rs%2015%20lakh%20money%20in%20every%20Indian's%20bank%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20PM%20Modi's%20jibe%20at%20Congress's%20achievements%20during%20the%20last%2070%20years%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20(Modi)%20became%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Gujarat%20and%20now%20the%20PM%20because%20the%20Congress%20had%20held%20the%20democracy%20and%20Constitution%20high.%20But%20you%20are%20now%20destroying%20the%20basics%20of%20democracy%20and%20the%20Constitution.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20the%20Congress%20has%20given%20rights%20to%20women%2C%20Dalits%2C%20tribals%20and%20the%20downtrodden%20by%20properly%20implementing%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClaiming%20that%20Odisha's%20ruling%20BJD%20and%20opposition%20BJP%20have%20solemnised%20a%20%26quot%3Blove%20marriage%26quot%3B%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20alleged%20that%20the%20two%20parties%20are%20looting%20Odisha%20and%20oppressing%20the%20poor%20people%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20claimed%20that%20while%20BJP%20and%20BJD%20are%20only%20with%20rich%20people%2C%20the%20Congress%20always%20stands%20by%20the%20poor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kharge%20said%20people%20lost%20their%20hard-earned%20money%20in%20the%20chit-fund%20scam%20and%20the%20mining%20loot%20is%20a%20regular%20phenomenon%20in%20the%20state.%20As%20both%20the%20parties%20are%20hand%20in%20glove%20with%20each%20other%2C%20culprits%20are%20not%20caught%2C%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kharge%20claimed%20that%20Congress%20gave%20Paradip%20Port%2C%20Rourkela%20Steel%20Plant%2C%20Chilka%20Naval%20Academy%2C%20Mancheshwar%20Rail%20Coach%20Factory%2C%20HAL%2C%20Ordnance%20factory%2C%20AIIMS%20and%20several%20educational%20institutions%20to%20the%20state.%20%26quot%3BBut%20today%20Patnaik%20ji%2C%20along%20with%20BJP%2C%20is%20allowing%20the%20natural%20wealth%20here%20to%20be%20looted%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20president%20said%20Pandit%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20held%20the%20last%20Congress%20session%20of%20his%20life%20in%20this%20land%20of%20Lord%20Jagannath%20in%201964.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPandit%20Nehru%20ji%20and%20Biju%20Patnaik%20ji%20were%20very%20good%20friends.%20He%20(Biju)%20believed%20in%20the%20ideology%20of%20Nehruji.%20But%20today's%20Patnaik%20(Naveen)%20believes%20in%20the%20ideology%20of%20BJP%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kharge%20said.%20Biju%20Patnaik%20was%20Naveen%20Patnaik's%20father%20and%20a%20former%20chief%20minister%20of%20Odisha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20naming%20anyone%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20also%20targeted%20Mr%20Patnaik's%20close%20aide%20and%20former%20IAS%20officer%20V%20K%20Pandian%2C%20who%20recently%20quit%20civil%20services%20and%20joined%20the%20ruling%20BJD.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAre%20there%20no%20leaders%20and%20officers%20from%20Odisha%20to%20advise%20the%20chief%20minister%20that%20someone%20has%20to%20be%20brought%20from%20another%20state%20to%20run%20the%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%20Pandian%20hails%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%202.36%20lakh%20vacancies%20in%20the%20state%20government.%20Odisha%20has%2029%20per%20cent%20ST%20and%2016%20per%20cent%20SC.%20Still%2C%20these%20people%20did%20not%20get%20any%20major%20job%20in%20the%20Patnaik%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kharge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20both%20the%20BJD%20and%20the%20BJP%20rejected%20allegations%20made%20by%20Mr%20Kharge.%20%26quot%3BKharge's%20visit%20and%20his%20statement%20will%20have%20no%20impact%20on%20the%20people%20of%20Odisha.%20The%20people%20here%20have%20great%20faith%20in%20Naveen%20Patnaik%20and%20therefore%20elected%20him%20for%20five%20consecutive%20times.%20People%20know%20who%20is%20developing%20Odisha%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20BJD%20leader%20and%20minister%20Atanu%20S%20Nayak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20chief%20whip%20Mohan%20Majhi%20of%20BJP%20said%20Mr%20Kharge's%20words%20may%20not%20have%20any%20impact%20on%20the%20people%20here%20as%20most%20of%20them%20appreciate%20PM%20Modi%20ji's%20works%20and%20performances.%20%26quot%3BBJD%20will%20lose%2C%20but%20the%20benefit%20will%20not%20go%20to%20Congress%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Majhi%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706587860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fqqbeckr_mallikarjun-kharge_625x300_28_January_24.jpeg%2