o%20%26quot%3Bbe%20with%20us%20in%20the%20coming%20years%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*The%20era%20of%20hyper-globalisation%20in%20global%20manufacturing%20is%20over%2C%20the%20report%20says.%20%26quot%3BIt%20does%20not%20mean%20that%20de-globalisation%20will%20be%20upon%20us%20any%20time%20soon%2C%20as%20countries%20are%20only%20now%20discovering%20the%20enormous%20integration%20of%20global%20supply%20chains%20that%20have%20taken%20place%20in%20the%20last%20few%20decades%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20says.%20So%2C%20an%20alternative%20to%20the%20globalisation%20of%20supply%20chains%20will%20take%20much%20longer%20to%20emerge%2C%20if%20it%20ever%20does%2C%20the%20report%20predicts.%20However%2C%20that%20will%20not%20deter%20governments%20from%20pursuing%20on-shoring%20and%20friend-shoring%20of%20production%20with%20a%20consequent%20impact%20on%20transportation%2C%20logistics%20costs%2C%20and%2C%20hence%2C%20the%20final%20prices%20of%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecent%20events%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20may%20have%20brought%20back%20concerns%20over%20reliance%20on%20global%20supply%20chains%2C%20further%20aggravating%20the%20slower%20growth%20in%20global%20trade%20in%202023.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20exporting%20one's%20way%20to%20growth%20will%20not%20be%20easy.%20This%20reinforces%20the%20need%20to%20lower%20logistics%20costs%20and%20invest%20in%20product%20quality%20to%20hold%20on%20to%20and%20expand%20market%20share%20in%20areas%20where%20India%20has%20an%20advantage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*Artificial%20Intelligence%20is%20another%20big%20trend%20to%20watch%20out%20for%2C%20the%20report%20says.%20%26quot%3BClosely%20related%20to%20this%20challenge%20is%20the%20advent%20of%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20with%20the%20profound%20and%20troubling%20questions%20it%20poses%20for%20growth%20in%20services%20trade%20and%20employment%20since%20technology%20might%20remove%20the%20advantage%20of%20cost%20competitiveness%20that%20countries%20exporting%20digital%20services%20enjoy%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*The%20third%20trend%2C%20and%20arguably%20the%20most%20important%2C%20is%20the%20energy%20transition%20challenge%2C%20the%20review%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConcerns%20over%20rising%20temperatures%20have%20led%20to%20a%20single-minded%20focus%20on%20reducing%20carbon%20emissions%20amidst%20the%20determination%20that%20the%20emission%20of%20greenhouse%20gases%2C%20particularly%20carbon%2C%20is%20the%20most%20significant%20factor.%20This%20has%20led%20to%20persistent%20demands%20from%20international%20organisations%20and%20advanced%20nations%20on%20developing%20nations%20to%20wean%20themselves%20off%20fossil%20fuels%20and%20switch%20to%20greener%20energy%20even%20as%20technological%20and%20resource%20obstacles%20remain%20and%20are%20not%20on%20offer%20from%20developed%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20says%20it%20is%20a%20reality%20that%2C%20in%20the%20short%20run%2C%20there%20is%20a%20trade-off%20between%20economic%20growth%20and%20energy%20transition.%20In%20a%20growth-challenged%20post-Covid%20global%20economy%2C%20countries%20can%20ill%20afford%20to%20sacrifice%20the%20former%20for%20the%20latter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20according%20to%20the%20overview%2C%20is%20walking%20the%20fine%20line%20between%20the%20two%20more%20skilfully%20than%20other%20nations%2C%20with%20installed%20non-fossil%20fuel-based%20power%20generation%20capacity%20running%20ahead%20of%20targets.%20Importantly%2C%20India's%20unwavering%20commitment%20to%20ensuring%20steady%20economic%20growth%20is%20generating%20resources%20for%20investment%20needed%20for%20climate%20change%20adaptation%2C%20building%20resilience%2C%20and%20mitigating%20emissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20says%20the%20Indian%20economy%20is%20better%20placed%20than%20ever%20to%20take%20on%20these%20three%20key%20challenges%20because%20of%20the%20policies%20adopted%20and%20implemented%20in%20the%20last%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706587500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fakklhcg_indian-economy-reuters_625x300_03_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2F3-trends-for-coming-years-highlighted-by-governments-economic-report-4958029%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20economy%20is%20likely%20to%20grow%20at%20over%207%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20next%20few%20years%20and%20the%20country%20is%20set%20to%20become%20the%20third%20largest%20economy%2C%20the%20government%20has%20said%20in%20a%20report%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Indian%20Economy%20-%20A%20Review%26quot%3B%20ahead%20of%20the%20interim%20Budget.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2F3-trends-for-coming-years-highlighted-by-governments-economic-report-4958029%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2F3-trends-for-coming-years-highlighted-by-governments-economic-report-4958029%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2F3-trends-for-coming-years-highlighted-by-governments-economic-report-4958029%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20Navy%20rescues%2019%20Pak%20nationals%20from%20Somali%20pirates%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706587336000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107248272%2Cimgsize-1440487.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fanti-piracy-operation-indian-navy-rescues-19-pakistani-nationals-from-somali-pirates%2Farticleshow%2F107247860.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Patrol%20vessel%20INS%20Sumitra%20rescued%20Fishing%20Vessel%20Al%20Naeemi%20%26amp%3B%20her%20crew%20(19%20Pakistani%20nationals)%20from%2011%20Somali%20pirates.%20In%20less%20than%2036%20hours%2C%20INS%20Sumitra%20has%20rescued%202%20hijacked%20fishing%20vessels.%20The%20Indian%20warship%20intercepted%20an%20Iranian-flagged%20