nancial%20sector%20have%20helped%20clean%20up%20the%20balance%20sheets%20of%20banks%20and%20corporates%20and%20emboldened%20banks%20to%20resume%20lending%20to%20all%20sectors%20of%20the%20economy.%20The%20unification%20of%20the%20domestic%20markets%20brought%20in%20by%20the%20adoption%20of%20the%20GST%20has%20incentivised%20production%20on%20a%20larger%20scale%2C%20and%20enhanced%20economic%20efficiency%20while%20reducing%20logistics%20costs%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20reads.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20adds%20that%20Centre's%20all-inclusive%20welfare%20approach%20is%20expected%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20expansion%20of%20the%20consumption%20base%20by%20enlarging%20the%20middle%20class.%20Despite%20challenges%20posed%20by%20the%20global%20health%20crisis%20and%20climate%20variability%2C%20the%20agriculture%20sector%20has%20displayed%20remarkable%20tenacity%20and%20resilience%2C%20it%20claims.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20robust%20Digital%20Public%20Infrastructure%20(DPI)%20has%20transformed%20the%20authentication%20ecosystem%2C%20reducing%20the%20cost%20of%20conducting%20electronic%20Know%20Your%20Customer%20(e-KYC).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20coupled%20with%20widespread%20internet%20connectivity%20and%20smartphones%2C%20rapid%20urbanisation%2C%20has%20propelled%20the%20country's%20e-commerce%20market%2C%20making%20India%20the%20third-largest%20fintech%20economy%20globally%20after%20USA%20and%20the%20UK.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706587200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fqgumto4o_nirmala-sitharaman-pti_625x300_31_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Findia-on-course-to-reach-7-trillion-economy-by-2030-finance-ministry-4957988%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ahead%20of%20the%20Interim%20Budget%2C%20a%20Finance%20Ministry%20report%20on%20Monday%20projected%20India's%20economic%20trajectory%20to%20potentially%20reach%20%247%20trillion%20by%202030.%22%2C%22