%20these%20incentives%20for%20people%20who%20want%20to%20gain%20notoriety%2C%20want%20to%20gain%20an%20audience%2C%20want%20to%20be%20the%20center%20of%20attention%2C%20to%20do%20this%20kind%20of%20stuff%2C%26quot%3B%20Mattei%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20has%20successfully%20framed%20himself%20as%20a%20victim%20who%20is%20constantly%20under%20attack%20and%20fighting%20for%20not%20only%20himself%20but%20for%20his%20supporters.%20So%20when%20he%20goes%20on%20the%20offensive%20and%20lobs%20attacks%20at%20his%20critics%20and%20accusers%2C%20he%20often%20gets%20a%20positive%20reaction%20from%20his%20supporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJones%20also%20stood%20to%20gain%20from%20spreading%20conspiracy%20theories%20about%20the%20Sandy%20Hook%20shooting%2C%20according%20to%20Mattei.%20During%20the%20defamation%20trial%2C%20Mattei%20told%20the%20jury%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fmarkets%2Frates-bonds%2Falex-jones-faces-second-sandy-hook-defamation-trial-connecticut-2022-09-13%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInfowars%20pulled%20in%20millions%20of%20followers%20off%20of%20the%20Sandy%20Hook%20lies%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20even%20made%20as%20much%20as%20%24800%2C000%20through%20product%20sales%20that%20followed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20is%20social%20media%20lifting%20up%20personalities%20that%20are%20willing%20to%20engage%20in%20defamatory%20conduct%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20making%20it%20so%20that%20when%20they%20do%2C%20the%20consequences%20for%20the%20defamed%20person%20are%20far%20greater.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20at%20Alex%20Jones%2C%20or%20you%20look%20at%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20because%20they%20have%20such%20a%20megaphone%2C%20their%20defamation%20power%20is%20a%20lot%20more%20significant%2C%26quot%3B%20Andrew%20Lieb%2C%20a%20New%20York%20litigation%20attorney%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELieb%20added%20it's%20not%20that%20any%20statement%20made%20on%20social%20media%20will%20automatically