actions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConsistent%20with%20that%20approach%2C%20we're%20requiring%20executives%20and%20people%20managers%20in%20the%20United%20States%20to%20be%20in%20the%20office%20at%20least%20three%20days%20per%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20told%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20change%20in%20policy%20marks%20a%20shift%20for%20IBM.%20In%20May%2C%20IBM%20CEO%20Arvind%20Krishna%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-05-03%2Fremote-work-can-hurt-your-career-ibm-ceo-says%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20wouldn't%20be%20forcing%20employees%20to%20return%20to%20the%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKrishna%2C%20however%2C%20said%20then%20that%20remote%20workers%20would%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fibm-ceo-remote-work-employees-careers-promotions-suffer-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%20the%20losing%20end%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20landing%20promotions%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20short%20term%2C%20you%20probably%20can%20be%20equally%20productive%2C%20but%20your%20career%20does%20suffer.%20Moving%20from%20there%20to%20another%20role%20is%20probably%20less%20likely%20because%20nobody's%20observing%20them%20in%20another%20context.%26quot%3B%20Krishna%20told%20Bloomberg%20in%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20will%20be%20tougher.%20Not%20impossible%2C%20but%20probably%20a%20lot%20tougher%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20IBM%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fibm-wants-managers-return-office-or-get-new-job-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706584409000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%