er%20offices%2C%20social%20media%2C%20advertisements%2C%20etc.%20to%20encourage%20more%20and%20more%20labourers%20to%20participate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELabourers%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20nation%2C%20skilled%20in%20shuttering%2C%20iron%20bending%2C%20ceramic%20tiling%20or%20plastering%2C%20are%20applying.%20The%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20released%20advertisements%20for%2010%2C000%20jobs%20in%20Israel%3A%203%2C000%20vacancies%20for%20a%20shuttering%20carpenter%2C%203%2C000%20for%20iron%20bending%2C%202%2C000%20for%20ceramic%20tiling%2C%20and%202%2C000%20for%20plastering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20government%20agency%20Population%2C%20Immigration%2C%20and%20Border%20Authority%20(PIBA)%20is%20offering%20a%20salary%20of%20between%20Rs%201%2C36%2C000%20and%20Rs%201%2C37%2C000%20per%20month%20to%20these%20labourers.%20The%20PIBA%20recruitment%20drive%20is%20being%20felicitated%20by%20the%20National%20Skills%20Development%20Corporation%20(NSDC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20Finance%20established%20the%20NSDC%20as%20a%20not-for-profit%20public%20limited%20company%20using%20a%20public-private%20partnership%20(PPP)%20model.%20The%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20through%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Skill%20Development%20and%20Entrepreneurship%20(MSDE)%2C%20holds%2049%25%20of%20the%20share%20capital%20of%20NSDC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20talked%20with%20some%20aspirants%20who%20came%20to%20ITI%20Lucknow%20to%20appear%20in%20the%20ongoing%20recruitment%20process%20for%20Israeli%20jobs.%20Pushpendra%20Kumar%2C%20a%20photographer%20from%20Sambhal%20district%2C%20was%20disappointed%20as%20the%20bank%20rejected%20his%20application%20for%20a%20loan%20to%20buy%20camera%20lenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20he%20learned%20about%20Israeli%20jobs%20through%20the%20newspaper%3B%20he%20went%20to%20the%20local%20labour%20office%20and%20registered%20his%20name%20there.%20Kumar%20said%20that%20he%20was%20sent%20to%20take%20part%20in%20the%20recruitment%20drive%20by%20the%20labour%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20I%20am%20putting%20my%20life%20in%20danger%20to%20earn%20money%20for%20my%20children%E2%80%99s%20future.%20I%20am%20well%20aware%20of%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20between%20Palestine%20and%20Israel%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kumar%20said.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20bank%20approves%20my%20small%20genuine%20loan%2C%20why%20do%20I%20intend%20to%20leave%20my%20kids%20alone%20at%20home%20and%20go%20to%20a%20war-torn%20nation%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F29174545%2F20240125_113634.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F29174545%2F20240125_113634.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F29174545%2F20240125_113634-300x135.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F29174545%2F20240125_113634-1024x462.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-694839%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22541%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20recruitment%20drive%20at%20ITI%20Lucknow.%20Photo%3A%20Asad%20Rizvi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimran%20Deep%20Singh%2C%20residing%20in%20Punjab%2C%20came%20to%20Lucknow%20to%20try%20to%20go%20to%20Israel%20to%20work%20as%20a%20construction%20labourer.%20Despite%20being%20aware%20of%20the%20conflict%2C%20Singh%2C%20who%20passed%20the%20metric%20exam%2C%20said%20he%20wishes%20to%20travel%20to%20Israel%20because%20he%20could%20not%20find%20employment%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20job%20aspirant%2C%20Deepak%20Kumar%2C%20said%20that%20he%20comes%20from%20a%20low-income%20household%20in%20the%20Jalaun%20district%2C%20where%20his%20father%20works%20as%20a%20labourer%20and%20makes%20bricks.%20%E2%80%9CI%20prefer%20to%20live%20in%20a%20red%20zone%20rather%20than%20live%20jobless%20at%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%E2%80%9CRs%201.36%20lakh%20is%20a%20big%20offer%20for%20me%20who%20has%20no%20work%20here.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20went%20on%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20decided%20to%20go%20there%20to%20earn%20money%20because%2C%20despite%20my%20best%20efforts%2C%20I%20was%20unable%20to%20find%20any%20work%20here%20so%20far.%20Whenever%20I%20return%20home%20from%20Israel%2C%20I%20will%20use%20my%20savings%20to%20launch%20my%20own%20business%20in%20my%20hometown.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshish%20Mishra%20spoke%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20while%20returning%20to%20his%20home%20in%20Azamgarh%20after%20appearing%20for%20an%20interview%20for%20a%20carpenter%E2%80%99s%20position.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20difficult%20to%20live%20with%20jobs%20that%20pay%20only%20Rs%208%2C000-10%2C000%20(per%20month)%20here%20at%20a%20time%20when%20inflation%20is%20very%20high.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20not%20sure%20when%20the%20interview%20results%20will%20be%20announced%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mishra%20ssaid.%20However%2C%20he%20was%20confident%20about%20getting%20work%20in%20Israel%2C%20although%20he%20was%20also%20unaware%20of%20the%20terms%20and%20conditions%20of%20the%20job%2C%20like%20the%20other%20aspirants.%20According%20to%20him%2C%20nobody%20told%20them%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20know%20that%20there%20is%20a%20risk%20to%20life%20there%20in%20Israel%2C%20but%20there%20is%20no%20bigger%20risk%20than%20poverty%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Satish%20Kumar%20Yadav%2C%20a%20carpenter%20who%20had%20earlier%20worked%20in%20Qatar.%20Yadav%20returned%20from%20Qatar%20in%20July%20last%20year%2C%20where%20he%20was%20earning%20more%20than%20Rs%2025%2C000%20per%20month.%20But%20since%20coming%20back%20from%20there%2C%20he%20has%20been%20jobless%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20opposition%20Congress%20attacked%20the%20Modi%20government%20and%20said%20the%20recruitment%20drives%20for%20jobs%20in%20war-hit%20Israel%20reflect%20that%20the%20country%20is%20passing%20through%20a%20time%20of%20massive%20unemployment%20and%20poverty%2C%20the%20same%20as%20seen%20in%20the%20pre-independence%20era%2C%20forcing%20labourers%20to%20look%20for%20job%20openings%20in%20red%20zones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Modi%20government%20was%20also%20criticised%20by%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20UP%20unit%20for%20its%20discrimination%20based%20on%20economic%20status.%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20is%20the%20Modi%20government%20sending%20poor%20nationals%20to%20work%20today%20when%20it%20evacuated%20Indian%20citizens%20from%20Israel%20during%20the%20war%20a%20few%20months%20ago%20through%20%E2%80%9COperation%20Ajay%E2%80%9D%3F%20No%20government%20should%20discriminate%20against%20people%20based%20on%20their%20economic%20situation.%20We%20want%20the%20hiring%20process%20to%20be%20immediately%20stopped%2C%E2%80%9D%20Congress%20leader%20Shahnawaz%20Alam%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlam%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20minority%20cell%2C%20said%20that%20in%20a%20prolonged%20conflict%20scenario%2C%20the%20proposal%20to%20send%20labourers%20would%20bring%20shame%20and%20establish%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20BJP%20government%20made%20the%20country%20poor%20and%20weak.%20The%20Congress%20also%20sent%20memoranda%20to%20governors%20via%20district%20authorities%20to%20stop%20the%20drive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F29174611%2F20240123_092439.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F29174611%2F20240123_092439.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F29174611%2F20240123_092439-300x135.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F29174611%2F20240123_092439-1024x462.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-694840%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22541%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20recruitment%20drive%20at%20ITI%20Lucknow.%20Photo%3A%20Asad%20Rizvi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChander%20Shekhar%2C%20UP%20state%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20All%20India%20Trade%20Union%20Congress%20(AITUC)%2C%20said%20this%20recruitment%20operation%20during%20the%20war%20was%20suspicious%20and%20also%20highlighted%20the%20inflation%20and%20unemployment%20prevalent%20in%20the%20country.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20the%20government%20was%20overlooking%20the%20security%20of%20migrant%20labourers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMazhar%20Azeez%20Khan%2C%20placement%20officer%20at%20ITI%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20on%20January%2023%2C%20a%20total%20of%20528%20students%20appeared%20for%20screening%2C%20of%20whom%20365%20passed%20the%20test.%20This%20figure%20increased%20on%20January%2024%2C%20when%20795%20candidates%20appeared%20in%20the%20test%20and%20531%20emerged%20successful.%20Similarly%2C%20on%20January%2025%2C%20the%20number%20of%20candidates%20appearing%20climbed%20to%201%2C023%2C%20out%20of%20which%20799%20passed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaj%20Kumar%20Yadav%2C%20principal%20of%20ITI%20Lucknow%2C%20said%20that%20the%20authorities%20in%20Israel%20and%20India%20both%20support%20the%20recruitment%20drive.%20Yadav%20also%20said%20they%20were%20facilitating%20recruiters%20from%20Israel%20looking%20for%2010%2C000%20skilled%20construction%20workers%20who%20could%20earn%20a%20respectable%20salary%20per%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYadav%20also%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20Israelis%20will%20give%20visa