20that%20this%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbackdoor%20entry%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20community%20into%20the%20OBC%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhujbal%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%2C%20which%20aligned%20with%20the%20ruling%20faction%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20party%20and%20the%20BJP%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20culmination%20of%20the%20Maratha%20quota%20stir%20has%20led%20to%20anxieties%20among%20existing%20OBC%20community%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20OBCs%20are%20having%20a%20feeling%20that%20they%20have%20lost%20their%20reservations%20as%20Marathas%20will%20take%20the%20benefits.%20I%20support%20giving%20a%20separate%20reservation%20to%20Marathas%2C%20but%20not%20sharing%20the%20existing%20OBC%20quota%20with%20them.%20Because%20once%20they%20become%20a%20part%20of%20the%20existing%20reservations%20for%20OBCs%2C%20only%20they%20will%20get%20the%20benefits%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20%3Cem%3EMidday%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mid-day.com%2Fmumbai%2Fmumbai-news%2Farticle%2Fbhujbals-critique-of-govt-not-official-stand-of-ncp-23332285%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20NCP%20(Ajit%20Pawar%20division)%20leader%20Praful%20Patel%20has%20said%20that%20Bhujbal%E2%80%99s%20criticism%20of%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%C2%A0%20is%20not%20the%20official%20stand%20of%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatel%20said%20Bhujbal%E2%80%99s%20stand%20was%20that%20of%20the%20Samata%20Parishad%2C%20the%20OBC%20group%20headed%20by%20him%2C%20and%20not%20of%20the%20NCP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhujbal%20said%20that%20retired%20Justice%20Sandeep%20Shinde%2C%20who%20heads%20the%20committee%20that%20will%20look%20into%20the%20Kunbi%20records%20of%20Marathas%2C%20receives%20an%20excessively%20high%20salary.%C2%A0He%20said%20that%20while%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20gets%20a%20salary%20of%20Rs%202.80%20lakh%2C%20Justice%20S