e%20different%20leaves%2C%20shoots%2C%20and%20structures.%20I%20was%20so%20fascinated%20by%20them%20that%20I%20decided%20to%20collect%20them%20one%20by%20one%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%2053-year-old%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20his%20paintings%2C%20Johnson%20travelled%20far%20and%20wide%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F195033%2Farunachal-pradesh-tourism-must-visit-culture-books-bamboo-cups%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econserve%20bamboo%20%3C%2Fa%3Evarieties.%20Today%2C%20he%20is%20a%20proud%20owner%20of%20the%2017-acre%20plantation%20that%20boasts%2010%2C000%20plants%20including%20a%20rare%20collection%20of%20142%20species%20collected%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FBamboo-1-1706104250.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Johnson%20travelled%20far%20and%20wide%20to%20conserve%20bamboo%20varieties%20beyond%20his%20paintings.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FBamboo-1-1706104250.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FBamboo-1-1706104250-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FBamboo-1-1706104250-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FBamboo-1-1706104250-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FBamboo-1-1706104250-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-339668%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EJohnson%20travelled%20far%20and%20wide%20to%20conserve%20bamboo%20varieties%20