c%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20India%2C%20seeing%20the%20limitless%20potential%20of%20the%20young%20entrepreneurs%20on%20the%20show.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20real%20takeaway%20from%20the%20show%20for%20me%20has%20been%20the%20fact%20that%20young%20Indians%20are%20truly%20limitless.%20And%20they%20are%20from%20Tier%203%20and%204%20towns%20of%20the%20country.%20They%20are%20doing%20so%20much%20with%20limited%20resources%20and%20under%20difficult%20circumstances.%20I%E2%80%99m%20buoyed%20about%20finding%20young%20talent%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20investor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20everyone%20young%20or%20old%2C%20Radhika%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFind%20your%20sky%20and%20learn%20to%20fly.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20world%20conspires%20to%20make%20you%20succeed%20if%20you%20want%20it%20hard%20enough.%20You%20can%E2%80%99t%20connect%20the%20dots%20but%20the%20dots%20start%20connecting.%20Each%20one%20of%20us%20is%20unique%20and%20different.%20Celebrate%20your%20perfections%20and%20imperfections%20and%20everything%20in%20between%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYour%20story%2C%20too%2C%20can%20have%20a%20happy%20ending.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706076791000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FGVZScZFGHVA%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D339578%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20being%20the%20'Girl%20With%20a%20Broken%20Neck'%20to%20selling%20her%20company%20to%20Edelweiss%20and%20becoming%20a%20judge%20on%20Shark%20Tank%20India%2C%20Radhika%20Gupta's%20journey%20has%20been%20truly%20incredible.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A147%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F339578%2Fradhika-gupta-shark-tank-india-judge-edelweiss-asset-management-broken-neck-ceo%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Man%20Takes%20You