s%20riding%20her%20bicycle%20and%20met%20with%20an%20accident%20that%20broke%20her%20left%20leg%2C%20Neeru%20says%2C%20ironically%20%E2%80%9Cit%20all%20started%20at%20that%20moment%E2%80%9D.%20Months%20of%20bedrest%20coupled%20with%20intense%20physiotherapy%20sessions%2C%20meant%20she%20was%20confined%20to%20a%20room%20while%20the%20other%20kids%20were%20at%20school.%20The%20absence%20of%20a%20TV%20or%20any%20form%20of%20entertainment%20compelled%20her%20to%20spend%20hours%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F297948%2Fyoutuber-mohit-manocha-traveling-desi-shares-how-to-become-travel-vlogger%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elooking%20out%20the%20window%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20her%20bedroom%2C%20where%20the%20blue%20expanse%20was%20her%20only%20view.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Ftravel-1-1706012506.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Neeru%20Saluja%20is%20a%20solo%20traveller%20who%20has%20been%20to%2080%20countries%20and%20counting%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Ftravel-1-1706012506.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Ftravel-1-1706012506-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Ftravel-1-1706012506-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Ftravel-1-1706012506-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Ftravel-1-1706012506-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-339535%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENeeru%20Saluja%20is%20a%20solo%20traveller%20who%20has%20been%20to%2080%20countries%